text: Deep Jwele Jaai means "I keep on lightning the lamp". It may refer to: *Deep Jwele Jaai, a 1959 Bengali film starring Uttam Kumar and Suchitra Sen. *Deep Jwele Jaai (TV series), a Bengali TV serial aired on Zee Bangla from 2016 to 2017. Category:Disambiguation pages
title: Deep Jwele Jaai (disambiguation)
